    All Classes and Interfaces

    Classes
    Class
    Description
    Board
    The Board class represents the game board for a strategy game.
    Cat
    The Cat class represents a cat piece in the game, extending the Piece class.
    Dog
    The Dog class represents a dog piece in the game, extending the Piece class.
    Game
    The Game class manages the overall game flow, player turns, piece selection, movement, and win conditions.
    HomeBase
    The HomeBase class represents a player's home base in the game.
    Lake
    The Lake class represents a lake tile on the game board.
    Main
    The Main class serves as the entry point of the game.
    Piece
    The Piece class is an abstract class that represents a piece in the game.
    Player
    Represents a player in the game.
    Trap
    The Trap class represents a trap tile on the game board.
